dct_title_s: Geologic map of western Santa Cruz Island, Santa Barbara, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology west Santa Cruz Island A & B quadrangles-DF-77
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights; depths shown by contours and soundings.
"Prepared with the support and cooperation of the Santa Cruz Island Foundation, Santa Barbara, California."
Includes 4 cross-sections, location map, note on sources of geology, ill., and 2 aerial photos.
Correlation chart, text and ill. on verso.
